just get a feelin' ♪

00:20.687 --> 00:23.156
♪ Like you need
some kind of change ♪

00:25.125 --> 00:28.562
♪ No matter what
the odds are this time ♪

00:28.595 --> 00:31.131
♪ Nothing's gonna
stand in my way ♪

00:31.164 --> 00:32.665
